%% UWWB Ontology - Overview
%% Stand: 2026-04-17 | Version: 1.0
graph LR
  %% === Kern-Domäne ===
  Company[Company]
  Company -->|PARENT_OF| Company
  Company -->|OWNS| Object[Object]
  Object -->|OF_TYPE| ObjectType[ObjectType]
  Object -->|HAS_RISK| Risk[Risk]
  Risk -->|PERIL_TYPE| PerilType[PerilType]
  Risk -->|COVERED_BY| Coverage[Coverage]
  Coverage -->|BASED_ON| Product[Product]
  Product -->|IN_LINE| Line[Line]
  Line -->|GOVERNED_BY| UnderwritingGuideline[UnderwritingGuideline]

  %% === Coverage-Lifecycle ===
  Coverage -->|REQUESTED_IN| Submission[Submission]
  Coverage -->|OFFERED_IN| Quote[Quote]
  Coverage -->|BOUND_IN| Policy[Policy]
  Coverage -->|DERIVED_FROM| Coverage

  %% === Workflow & Vertrieb ===
  Tender[Tender] -->|ISSUED_BY| Broker[Broker]
  Tender -->|FOR_COMPANY| Company
  Submission -->|IN_TENDER| Tender
  Submission -->|SUBMITTED_BY| Broker
  Submission -->|COVERS_COMPANY| Company
  Submission -->|ADDRESSED_TO| Insurer[Insurer]
  Submission -->|HAS_OBJECT| Object
  Submission -->|APPROVED_BY| User[User]
  Submission -->|PRODUCED| Quote
  Quote -->|FOR_PRODUCT| Product
  Quote -->|UNDERWRITTEN_BY| Insurer
  Quote -->|REALIZED_AS| Policy
  Policy -->|ON_PRODUCT| Product
  Policy -->|UNDERWRITTEN_BY| Insurer
  Policy -->|AMENDED_BY| Endorsement[Endorsement]
  Policy -->|HAS_CLAIM| Claim[Claim]
  Claim -->|ON_OBJECT| Object
  Claim -->|FOR_RISK| Risk
  Claim -->|AFFECTS_COVERAGE| Coverage

  %% === KI-Schicht ===
  Submission -->|HAS_DOCUMENT| Document[Document]
  Submission -->|PROCESSED_IN| ExtractionRun[ExtractionRun]
  ExtractionRun -->|USED_DOCUMENT| Document
  ExtractedField[ExtractedField] -->|EXTRACTED_IN| ExtractionRun
  ExtractedField -->|FROM_DOCUMENT| Document
  ExtractedField -->|POPULATES| Object
  ExtractedField -->|POPULATES| Risk
  ExtractedField -->|POPULATES| Coverage

  %% === Assessment & Audit ===
  Assessment[Assessment] -->|ASSESSES| Submission
  Assessment -->|APPLIES_GUIDELINE| UnderwritingGuideline
  User -->|AUTHORED| UnderwritingGuideline
  User -->|MEMBER_OF| Line
  AuditEvent[AuditEvent] -->|ON_SUBMISSION| Submission
  AuditEvent -->|BY_USER| User
  AuditEvent -->|AFFECTS_FIELD| ExtractedField
